blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁你連死都死得冇意義喎<br />\n冇意義咁生 都可以有意義咁死</blockquote><br />\n你死先啦咁，正黑心鬼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你自己講嫌命長，人地叫你要死得有意義你又話人黑心鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我嫌命長就要去死嗎？呀黑心鬼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你理解下人地句說話先啦，<br />\n佢講你而家死左都一啲意義都無，<br />\n咁不如活得有意義啲咁死（可能幫到其他人etc)<br />\n即係間接叫你唔好死，<br />\n而唔係叫你而家即刻去死呀醒目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實你唔好嫌命長啦你學下用腦先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定女人真係咁唔講道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd1b5975f5209894a1b55706faa5e7fab7b43654","tid":358421,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T18:19:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁你連死都死得冇意義喎<br />\n冇意義咁生 都可以有意義咁死</blockquote><br />\n你死先啦咁，正黑心鬼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你自己講嫌命長，人地叫你要死得有意義你又話人黑心鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我嫌命長就要去死嗎？呀黑心鬼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你理解下人地句說話先啦，<br />\n佢講你而家死左都一啲意義都無，<br />\n咁不如活得有意義啲咁死（可能幫到其他人etc)<br />\n即係間接叫你唔好死，<br />\n而唔係叫你而家即刻去死呀醒目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實你唔好嫌命長啦你學下用腦先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定女人真係咁唔講道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收聲啦，係度教訓我，最想推我去死果個人咪就係你囉"},{"pid":"c42362f5206dcec96fd4191a287e5dc81eab3da7","tid":358421,"uid":36722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T18:47:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486611e412ad3da058b26505c01e6fff003e39bf","tid":358421,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T19:04:35.000Z","msg":"有時都會咁諗"},{"pid":"5a6b6b434f8cbf7bdfedc445156919452eced3ad","tid":358421,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T19:12:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb7149ee567315dff2e4757ed180e9b74965d51","tid":358421,"uid":863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T19:20:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"641932fb7063e5653aa9c74e3cba71b60a4d846d","tid":358421,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T19:21:10.000Z","msg":"我都是咁諗 真是好灰"}]}